item.title: Minesweeper A Classic Puzzle Game
item.description: During the game Find Numbers, you will have to find all the indicated numbers in the image dedicated to the animals from the jungle. Use the magnifying glass to examine every corner of the picture. As soon as you see a number, immediately click on it. For the correct choice you will receive reward points.
